2) cs.MM (Multimedia) is also likely as the paper deals with multi-valued images and real-time video segmentation. 
3) cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possibility as the paper discusses the use of a user-defined distance measure for segmentation criteria. 
4) cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possibility as the paper proposes a modified CCA algorithm. 
5) cs.GR (Graphics) is a possibility as the paper deals with image segmentation.
